!longread_umi_L3Rseq/**
!UMIC-seq_L3Rseq/
!UMIC-seq_L3Rseq/**

# Pipeline runtime code
!L3Rseq
!config.sh
!scripts/
!scripts/**
!resources/
!resources/**
!igv_viewer/
!igv_viewer/**
igv_viewer/node_modules/
